@NODE Introduction "What it actually does..."

	Introduction
	============

  This blanker shuffles the screen around.

@ENDNODE


@NODE Interface "Configuration preferences..."

	Interface
	=========

@{b}           Save @{ub}- save and use the current settings.

@{b}            Use @{ub}- use the current settings.

@{b}           Test @{ub}- test the blanker under the current settings

@{b}         Cancel @{ub}- cancel all changes.


@{b}           Rows @{ub}- how many rows vertically.
                  @{i}Default: 8.@{ui}

@{b}           Cols @{ub}- how many colums horizontally.
                  @{i}Default: 8.@{ui}

@{b}      Grid Type @{ub}- set how should the grid be drawn.
                  May choose None, Single Lines, or System Beveled Box.
                  @{i}Default: System Beveled Box.@{ui}

@{b}  Shuffle Speed @{ub}- set how fast the squares should be moved around.
                  @{i}Default: 5.@{ui}

@{b}     Multi Move @{ub}- unimplemented.
                  @{i}Default: Off.@{ui}


@ENDNODE


